column5: I'm logged in for one thread and then logged out for the next.  I can only read what I read yesterday.  Anything new is gone?  What's going on?  Any ideas?  Hopefully I'll see them.
Not having any problems here Scott. Computer virus may be a possibility.
Hmmm...things are ok here.  First thing I'd do is re-boot the computer.  Second thing would be to clear the internet cookies and then try again.
No viruses.  Did what you said Cliff and it seems to be working.  Thanks.  Odd that it was just this site though?
I just found out they had internet on computers now, so I thought I would try.
